-- Chile Pensions Regulator Publishes New Currency Hedging Rules
-- B y   S e b a s t i a n   B o y d
-- 2012-06-29T16:24:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/chile-pensions-regulator-publishes-new-currency-hedging-rules.html
Chile ’s pensions supervisor
published new  currency hedging  rules for the country’s pension
funds.  The rules affect investments in bonds and equities outside
Chile, the supervisor said today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
